title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Robinson R44 Raven II helicopter  - version 1.0 beta
description:
In this video we will look at the Robinson R44 Raven II helicopter which has been now released as official beta version. In this video we will look at how to install the helicopter and all the prereqs first. Once we completed that part we will look both from the external and interval view to the enhancements made before we are going to start the engines and take off.

0:00 title screen
0:10: look at liveries and discuss changes
1:40 installation of helicopter and prereqs
7:10 start of internal/external review
13:52 start the engines 
20:13 take off

If you also want to give the Robinson R44 Raven II helicopter a try download it the helicopter and the prereqs via the links below:
